data.eml:eml: A new species of Phycodes from China (Lepidoptera: Sesioidea: Brachodidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kallies, Axel, Wang, Min, Arita, Yutaka (2011): A new species of Phycodes from China (Lepidoptera: Sesioidea: Brachodidae). Zootaxa 2797: 54-56, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.277024
